name: Spooky Uni
description: Spooky Uni is an innovative project that will revolutionize the world of DeFi. Spooky Uni, I have been waiting for this moment for many years. Creating an ecosystem with bitcoin funds, initially it may seem like memecoin, but you will see what will happen. 0% tax token with ownership renounced of the contract to give all the trust to the holders and to ensure that no one can modify the contract or abuse the power of the project. The community is the important thing here.
